# Documentation Rules

type: Auto Attached
globs: ["docs/**"]

## Always
- Start file with `Version:` header (semver or date)
- Keep sections: Purpose, How to run, Change log (link to PR)
- Use clear, concise language
- Include examples where helpful
- Update version header when making changes

## Never
- Leave documentation outdated after API changes
- Remove version headers
- Include sensitive information
- Create documentation without clear purpose